        "subject": "LU-591 MRP-139 1.8->2.x lustre migration tool",
        "message": "LU-591 MRP-139 1.8->2.x lustre migration tool\n\nConvert on-disk data structures on MDS of Lustre FS 1.8 to Lustre FS\n2.x ones in-place:\n- assign true FIDs, stored in LMA EA;\n- assign parent FIDs, stored in Link EA;\n- assign children FIDs, stored in directory entries;\n- create OI so that FIDs point to the proper inode numbers;\n\nChange-Id: I5002995beacde3b6e18a4a7f316a7d10be9dc12d\nReviewed-by: Nathan Rutman <Nathan_Rutman@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey_lyashkov@xyratex.com>\nSigned-off-by: Vitaly Fertman <vitaly_fertman@xyratex.com>\n"
      },
